		(property "Description" "DNP failsafe bias insurance (panel review 3.a, 2026-07-20): pull-up RS485+ (A) to +3V3. THVD1429 integrated open/short/idle failsafe makes bias normally unnecessary; populate R4+R5 only if idle-bus noise is ever observed. 390R pair gives ~236mV across 60R differential load at 3.3V. PARKED UNWIRED - to be wired DNP by hand."
			(at 184.15 57.15 0)
